
# Title: Summary, imperative, start upper case, do'nt end with a period
# Format: <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# No more than 50 chars---------------------------
#
# Type List
# (from https://github.com/angular/angular.js/blob/master/DEVELOPERS.md#type)
#
# feat    : A new feature
# fix     : A bug fix
# docs    : Documentation only changes
# styles  : Changes that do not affect the meaning of the code
#           (white-spacing, formatting, missing semi-colons, etc)
# refactor: A code change that neither fixes bug nor adds a feature
# perf    : A code change that improves performance
# test    : Adding missing or correcting existing tests
# chore   : Changes to the build process or auxiliary tools  and libraries such
#           as documentation generation

# Remember blank line between title and body

# Body: Explain *what* and *why* (not *how*). Include task ID
# Wrap at 72 chars------------------------------------------------------
